{"tid":856911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食人滅世野豬屠城 !兩長者遭噬大腿浴血 300磅野豬連襲3人","createTime":"2018-10-11T00:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T07:25:25.000Z","uid":65346,"like":8,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f6e95e9b5253bd5bd898b619dd490b03bd46ef","tid":856911,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:02:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181011/20519496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F20519496&d=UOW%2B3jzwuZjdo5wYyXMmscmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=637bddbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F20519496&h=1ca638a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181011/20519496</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港再發生野豬傷人事件，黃大仙富山邨有女保安員昨晨在屋邨公廁外，遭一頭長有獠牙的成年野豬撞倒並咬傷腳，傷者高聲呼救，驚動男街坊以雨傘驅趕野豬，但他亦被野豬撞傷。野豬其後逃至約百米外再撞跌一名老翁，並咬傷其右大腿，之後往山上逃去。兩名被咬傷者分別送院檢查，遭撞傷街坊自行離開，當局事後派員到場搜索野豬無果。<br />\n記者：黃江奇　劉永明<br />\n<br />\n受傷女保安員姓陳（65歲），昨晨近7時放工行經富山邨富信樓地下公廁時，一頭重約<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">300磅</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 長有獠牙的野豬突向陳婦衝來，將她撞跌後狂噬其右腿，陳婦腿部登時血流如注，高聲呼救，一名男街坊見狀揮動手上雨傘嘗試驅趕野豬，但反被野豬撞傷。<br />\n<br />\n食過人血,一定同豬隊友開心 share, 好快傾巢而出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7765cbf67159db69b9c207f4fee7f5e9164685d7","tid":856911,"uid":65346,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:03:41.000Z","msg":"被咬嘅人,又會變豬頭人,四圍咬 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c813f6ffe4d262cd470bbe3ce5b5421c8360f70c","tid":856911,"uid":65346,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/4e/Bebop_and_Rocksteady.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F4%2F4e%2FBebop_and_Rocksteady.png&h=e0b4dfec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsample"},{"pid":"4fa545f763fc12ce7d546c19b65fb71fc6aed98e","tid":856911,"uid":65346,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:05:11.000Z","msg":"右面係比犀牛咬過嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4e4c1579c872f8d04533d72f04586240106d37","tid":856911,"uid":121831,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:06:36.000Z","msg":"通職題：野豬重啲定catgirl重啲？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-01-19/656/20170119005039.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-01-19%2F656%2F20170119005039.jpg&h=88359dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/080634_3b1e3fd27e66e15be9bbe70efee7831e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F080634_3b1e3fd27e66e15be9bbe70efee7831e.png&h=09c20e08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"974bd7e99f69d282822734d07fe19545a7fa8d1d","tid":856911,"uid":67500,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:07:32.000Z","msg":"殺左隻豬啦<br />\n<br />\n放豬歸山，後患無窮"},{"pid":"2782ee2d79735dcff01662008704ca22a244990f","tid":856911,"uid":33206,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:07:49.000Z","msg":"屌